@Zeneca_33 Peak Design's Everyday bag is really rigid and bulky. Was nice for commuting, not ideal for traveling.

Minaal's Daily is nice, might be too soft/small for some.

Currently liking Black Ember's Shadow as a "grab and go on the plane/car" bag, but their Forge has much more space.

@realhumankinder @coolcatsnft This doesn't make sense whatsoever. 

The `onlyOwner` modifier immediately causes the function to fail.

The EVM wouldn't allow this to be blocking any sort of switch. The only bottleneck would be gas prices. Anyone trying to flood this would just burn gas for nothing.
